data.description: New..... fixtures, tile, laminate, lights, plantation closet doors, garage door opener, screens, landscaping, and outdoor lighting. 2014 Roof. The dining room room overlooks the beautiful open floor plan with a huge great room and galley style kitchen with black and stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Separate laundry room. Remodeled guest bath.  The master bedroom has 2 walk in closets, a tiled walk-in shower, double sinks and a slider to the pool area where the deck was just freshly painted. Outside that is the yard with a sprinkler system on a well and a lemon and orange tree fenced for your privacy.  The home also offers an insulated garage door, gutters and hurricane shutters. So no carpet!!!!  All this located in the very desirable subdivision of Deerwood at River Ridge. Home Warranty!  This home will surely not last long come see why!!! If buyer uses our preferred lender, Jay Bruno from Supreme Lending, a $2,000 credit will be given towards closing costs as well as a free appraisal.
